@jiamin13579 you might want to take a look at https://iceberg.apache.org/docs/latest/evolution/#partition-evolution.

> Partition evolution is a metadata operation and does not eagerly rewrite files

So what you most likely would want to do in your case is to rewrite data files after you changed the partitioning
